## Overview

Displays a sequence illustration.
If number isn't set, it will display one at random.

## Usage

### Example

```tsx
export default () => <kurrent-sequence />;
```



## Properties

| Property | Attribute | Description                     | Type                  | Default     |
| -------- | --------- | ------------------------------- | --------------------- | ----------- |
| `number` | `number`  | Select the sequence to display. | `number \| undefined` | `undefined` |
